Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【Dialogue】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.05,0:04:48.98,title,NTP,0,0,0,,凉风飒飒{\fad(1300,0)}{\pos(512,415)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.73,0:00:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后啊 祐麒突然说 你变坚强了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.82,0:00:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说 我有点着急了呢 什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.04,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是您的弟弟对祐巳大人有点嫉妒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.98,0:00:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫉妒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.04,0:00:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在聪明可爱 性格又开朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可挑剔 完美的姐姐身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你只能是彻底欺负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是俯首称臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.25,0:00:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是视而不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.79,0:00:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就无法维持自己的存在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美的姐姐什么的 可南子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.87,0:00:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人您最有魅力的地方就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.12,0:00:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没发现自己是多么有魅力的女孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.50,0:01:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.51,0:01:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人 请不要做这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.46,0:01:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.87,0:01:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可南子 你来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.40,0:01:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安 黄蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.90,0:01:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你一直来打理呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.60,0:01:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 我才刚到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.89,0:01:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是发现祐巳大人已经打扫得差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.92,0:01:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您要喝点麦茶吗? 黄蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.73,0:01:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 令大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.53,0:01:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扫的活 不是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.99,0:02:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女孩是为了祐巳才站出来帮忙的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这个到处为了学园祭忙成一团的时期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来义务帮忙这么难得的人可不好找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.26,0:02:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.40,0:02:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.91,0:02:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿过高大的校门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.33,0:02:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让裙子上的褶痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.82,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让白色的水手领翻起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒缓地行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.90,0:03:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.66,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 祐巳也已经是有威望的人了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.17,0:04:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂热的一年级崇拜者像倒贴女似的跟在身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊? 刚才说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 祥子还没注意到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二学期开始后时常会过来玩的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆明了目标是祐巳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 目标是我什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.01,0:05:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 个子高高的头发超长的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.94,0:05:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.10,0:05:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次我看到她在走廊下和祐巳谈话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.25,0:05:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我一走近就忽然走开不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子 该不是你用可怕的眼神瞪着她了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.97,0:05:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对随便和可爱的祐巳搭话的谜之低年级生心生嫉妒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.21,0:05:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要开玩笑了好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.40,0:05:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 原来那个女孩是一年级生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是乃梨子的朋友吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同班同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你知道的说说看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.77,0:05:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年级椿组 细川可南子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在班上的表现并不像外表那么突出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.48,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息的时候也大多是自己一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.68,0:06:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独来独往一匹狼的感觉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.84,0:06:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一匹狼? 那不正和乃梨子很像嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.28,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃梨子没和她说过话吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.59,0:06:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班级事务方面的交谈还好 但闲聊就完全搭不上话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.63,0:06:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子呢 她看起来挺热心的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 几乎可以用天敌来形容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.56,0:06:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么怎么办? 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.93,0:06:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有考虑过让她当妹妹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹…吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.55,0:06:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何? 明白我去年的心情了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.36,0:06:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明不明白的 去年这时候我们还不太亲近所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该是时候了 由乃也好 祐巳也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.86,0:06:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没人认个妹妹的话真有点难办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.80,0:07:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 该是时候让我们安心一下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.96,0:07:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 祐巳和那个女孩开始亲近起来的契机究竟是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.52,0:07:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我完全想不起来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.65,0:07:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.18,0:07:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是图书馆的还书期限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.09,0:07:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不要紧了 快去图书馆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.62,0:07:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃和志摩子你们也可以回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就和祐巳一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.15,0:07:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.67,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想过要她当妹妹的话 还是先说清楚比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.68,0:07:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是可南子她从来没说过想做妹妹什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.51,0:07:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不一定要勉强拒绝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果祐巳想要她当妹妹的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.98,0:08:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 开了让倒贴女做妹妹的先例的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后不就麻烦了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.46,0:08:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 说到倒贴女的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.88,0:08:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了 嘿嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事件在某天的午休时间发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.85,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.55,0:08:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.98,0:08:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人不可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.26,0:08:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人才是 看不到有什么同伴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.92,0:08:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我妈她忘了做饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当只有配菜 所以我过来买面包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没问你这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.62,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗? 一直都带便当的祐巳大人为什么会到面包房来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想过这样的问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也太自命不凡了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.90,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世间可没这么关注祐巳大人的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子真是的 好冷淡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.76,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳觉得寂寞了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.89,0:09:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是好久都不来蔷薇馆玩了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社团活动很忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.98,0:09:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有其它不爽的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也来玩玩嘛 祥子大人也一定会高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.95,0:09:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我而不爽的话 可以在我不在的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想看到的人不是祐巳大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,细川可南子 我实在无法喜欢这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.69,0:09:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人 还不快些 面包要卖光了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.49,0:09:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.66,0:09:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有三明治吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿个果酱面包给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都带便当的祐巳大人为什么会到面包房来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈她早上忘了做饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这可麻烦了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.84,0:10:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人喜欢哪种面包?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪种啊 没有什么特别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就去挑几个合适的买吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可南子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有配菜的 只要买一个就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.97,0:10:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当快啊 插队了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个来 您想要哪个面包啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.80,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选不出哪个好 总之把中意的全买下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.06,0:10:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少钱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 这个果酱面包是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.65,0:10:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说那个 这些一共多少?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.00,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.73,0:10:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子不是当自己的午饭才买的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我全买下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.37,0:10:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.53,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 多少钱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我自作主张买的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没理由让祐巳大人来承担多余的部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如这些都给您吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.83,0:11:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.45,0:11:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了不要钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.30,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啦 我也说了不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学 还有这位同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.61,0:11:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微冷静一下 看看自己周围的情况如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.66,0:11:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 祐巳同学出一个面包的价钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.27,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的两个我买下了 好不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.61,0:11:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是打扰大家了 请继续享受美好的午休时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢您帮忙解围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但三个面包都是为了祐巳大人买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道是那样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学也知道的 是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.45,0:12:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茑子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.85,0:12:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢 帮大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.68,0:12:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 那么能陪我一会儿吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着这些面包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拿面包做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.96,0:12:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是用来贿赂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.73,0:12:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贿赂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了就会想要吃点甜食的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧 要我帮什么忙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.76,0:12:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 刚才祐巳同学她出了点小麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概马上就会传到真美同学的耳里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.65,0:12:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个能不能别登到莉莉安瓦版上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.18,0:13:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了商量这事而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.89,0:13:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什么大事 买东西争着付钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.83,0:13:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一方请客一方推辞 这种程度的事情而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美同学 有特大新闻!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.94,0:13:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红蔷薇花蕾和一年级的妹妹候补在面包房大吵了一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.42,0:13:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止她们的是摄影部的武岛茑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.21,0:13:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 贵安 我是摄影部的武岛茑子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学和妹妹候补大吵一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里是小麻烦 这不是大新闻嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.10,0:13:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦 是不是候补 听听祐巳同学的说法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.95,0:13:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都还没…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认她做妹妹吗? 不认吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.91,0:13:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美同学 冷静冷静~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.15,0:13:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 可南子同学好像没有做红蔷薇花蕾妹妹的打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.99,0:13:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她本人是这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人? 细川可南子她自己说的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 试着直接采访了本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.55,0:14:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否要做红蔷薇花蕾的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.62,0:14:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 然后呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一笑置之了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.56,0:14:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没这么庸俗的奢望 这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.86,0:14:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 我问要是祐巳大人强烈希望的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回答的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会拒绝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.73,0:14:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 祐巳在学校里也不容易呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不容易啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.21,0:14:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐麒不是吗? 各个方面来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.26,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 最近爱丽丝说有被什么东西跟着的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.55,0:14:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小林说自己好像被谁给看上了 正得意着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 虽然最近都见过这两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没听他们提到这种事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.06,0:15:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭都快到了还…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.63,0:15:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 蔷薇大人中有没有怕高的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.94,0:15:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.89,0:15:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 大家干劲十足 正在做很高大的了望台呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.69,0:15:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了望台?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.63,0:15:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 蔷薇大人们的裁判席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就是所谓的花寺合战的项目吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.17,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有怕高的人的话 就不得不改造了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.04,0:15:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以早点问清楚比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我去打听一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高的地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 祥子她比较不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.95,0:15:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.98,0:15:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.97,0:15:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前说过不坐云霄飞车 就想到也许是这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 白色情人节兼祐巳的生日礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过到游乐园约会半天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是一直都没去成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子对乘坐交通工具也不太行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.92,0:15:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长距离的话 还会晕车呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修学旅行来回坐飞机的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.34,0:16:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上机前喝了晕车药然后睡觉 吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又喝药 睡觉 吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在飞机里经过祥子身旁时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.40,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都只看到一副流着口水的睡相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.45,0:16:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁流口水了?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是打个比方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦不 应该说是夸张吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.99,0:16:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 不要相信令的鬼话哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.15,0:16:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.60,0:16:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 怎么说到飞机的话题上去的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺学院的学园祭的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.34,0:16:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁判席变成比预定更高的了望台了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.68,0:16:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 现在还能再修改方案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.07,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 预算也是有限的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会给对方增加麻烦 唉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.79,0:16:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 由不才我来代替姐姐大人到了望台上面去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.55,0:16:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你上去的话 还是我自己来好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 上到哪里去都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.77,0:17:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红蔷薇的工作 我会好好示范给你看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要乖乖看着就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.24,0:17:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 高度大概有二楼的窗户到地面那么高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就完全没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 这不也是二楼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.49,0:17:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从二楼的窗户看出去一点都没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.46,0:17:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会认为我只能上到校舍的三楼而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.45,0:17:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.37,0:17:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再说这说那了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.43,0:17:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟祐麒说这边已经了解了就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.58,0:17:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 工作工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 祥子 这些拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.22,0:17:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变厉害了呢 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵祥子方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没这样打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.87,0:17:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却无意间像是把祥子大人推到了高处的了望台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就在不久之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.54,0:18:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却体会到了突然被从高处推下的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了? 茑子同学 还不回家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.29,0:18:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我的话是因为要来拿忘了的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 该说是不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.07,0:18:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了? 嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些 不都是我的照片嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.83,0:18:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备学园祭中要的祐巳同学的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.30,0:18:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影部用来展出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要拍我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.09,0:18:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年祐巳同学和祥子大人的特大照片很受好评啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.12,0:18:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此决定今年也从红蔷薇姐妹身上取材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.37,0:18:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 茑子同学在烦恼什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出在烦恼的样子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.19,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了? 拍摄的对象有什么问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常自然的姿态 给人很好的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 是什么地方不行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可惜 只好连底片一起处理掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.65,0:19:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个送到新闻部手上就不知道会发生什么事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.45,0:19:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有点可怕的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不该告诉你吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没关系 谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.14,0:19:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和姐姐大人商量一下比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.65,0:19:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 又不想把事情弄大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 问问祐麒看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.58,0:20:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能想到什么好的解决办法就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.45,0:20:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 想起有事情要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又忘了东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.91,0:20:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.66,0:20:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图书馆的还书期限还没到吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我先走一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯过来和我说话的话就好办了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.07,0:20:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.29,0:20:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.83,0:20:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备回家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.25,0:20:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.50,0:20:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 有背后灵跟着你呢 知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背后灵什么的 真失礼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经发觉了啊 真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 要让她跟到哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先到校门再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校门那有什么准备吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.61,0:21:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会碍事的 看着行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我说不 圣大人也不会乖乖待着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.01,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 答对了~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.47,0:21:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然来的是柏木同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.23,0:21:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一样可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.24,0:21:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有点过分了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.91,0:21:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个暂且不提 这背后灵是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.56,0:21:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小麒说的类型完全不同啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.97,0:21:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.21,0:21:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么银杏王子会出现在这里? 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.38,0:21:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏木同学是故意和我装作很亲密的样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.84,0:21:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我弟弟拜托他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.97,0:21:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是我自告奋勇来的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.64,0:21:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到学生会里小麒他们在密谈着些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.69,0:22:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问出原因之后就让他们把这好差事让给我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.05,0:22:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业了还在学校里出没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道这样的毕业生可是最让人讨厌的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.91,0:22:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学弟们拜托我去的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.23,0:22:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.63,0:22:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 推理小说同好会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.42,0:22:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 偏离话题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.14,0:22:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么推理一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.34,0:22:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是让祐巳背上的座敷童子看到她和男子亲密的样子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.94,0:22:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都能推理得到吧 这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.76,0:22:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.79,0:22:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就看她会如何行动了 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.24,0:23:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有话对我说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.60,0:23:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的花寺学园祭 请不要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.82,0:23:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.97,0:23:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我失礼 祐巳大人还不是蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.52,0:23:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定可以不用去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.17,0:23:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不想让我去那里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.99,0:23:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那里有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.51,0:23:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.65,0:23:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那里都是男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.81,0:23:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人们都会窥伺祐巳大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.28,0:23:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.91,0:23:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 祐巳大人很可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.18,0:23:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人太没有防备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.23,0:23:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是纯真的缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.42,0:23:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人来搭讪的话半点戒心都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.84,0:23:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人可是你小心再小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.57,0:23:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是防不胜防的危险存在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.20,0:24:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 跟踪和我接触过的男人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.16,0:24:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天 我和柏木同学分开后 你跟踪他了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.46,0:24:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.49,0:24:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的弟弟后来紧跟着你 看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.70,0:24:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝和小林同学你也跟踪过了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.43,0:24:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么? 比起我的话来更相信男人说的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.26,0:24:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人什么的 是我的弟弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.18,0:24:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌男人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.16,0:24:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.05,0:24:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人是最低贱的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.41,0:24:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是有低贱的人 可是并不是全部啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.39,0:24:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子不也有父亲嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.51,0:24:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.31,0:24:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种人 不是我父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.31,0:24:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人是要为男人辩护吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.21,0:24:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳大人应该始终像天使一般存在着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.73,0:25:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不看肮脏的男人一眼 一直保持纯白的少女模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.83,0:25:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在圣母玛莉亚的学园里微笑着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.88,0:25:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.36,0:25:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也喜欢这个学校 也想能一直停留在这段时间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.38,0:25:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但随着年龄增长 很多东西都会发生变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.03,0:25:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的是现在的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.52,0:25:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使那样我也是一个人 也有自己的人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.66,0:25:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很感谢可南子担心我的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.61,0:25:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但去花寺帮忙是我的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.32,0:25:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能够做出和年龄相适合的判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.91,0:25:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有希望过您做那样的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.47,0:25:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有希望过 是什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.19,0:25:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看到的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.44,0:25:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样在温室中含苞待放的红蔷薇的花蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.00,0:25:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从第一眼看到祐巳大人开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.10,0:26:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就确信您才是足以作为莉莉安女学园象征的无垢的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.75,0:26:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是像可南子所想的那样夸张的人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.00,0:26:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是抱着这样的印象注视着祐巳大人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.47,0:26:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当之无愧的红蔷薇花蕾 大家憧憬的对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.10,0:26:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.92,0:26:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 是在演戏骗人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:29.18,0:26:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说不是这样的话 那也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.35,0:26:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使演戏也应该直到最后都给大家留下好印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.60,0:26:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做不是祐巳大人风格的轻率的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.28,0:26:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出不适合祐巳大人说的言语?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:46.29,0:26:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要背叛大家的期待!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.67,0:26:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得相当过分呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.01,0:26:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己随便喜欢上别人还跟在身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.11,0:26:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却因为不是自己所想像的那样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.26,0:27:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以伤害对方了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.53,0:27:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的觉得有这样的道理吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:05.19,0:27:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.92,0:27:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头脑发热也要有个限度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.50,0:27:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不算是这个世界的法律吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.86,0:27:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:24.98,0:27:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.62,0:27:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣大人昨天傍晚打电话过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.09,0:27:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点在意 要我留意你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:33.42,0:27:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都对祐巳的变化很敏感呢 圣大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.31,0:27:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在最希望能陪在身边的毫无疑问是祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:44.63,0:27:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:46.44,0:27:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的风格是怎么一回事呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:49.27,0:27:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都没意识到过自己在别人眼里是什么印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.18,0:27:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是很好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.67,0:28:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是时常会想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:06.92,0:28:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任性 傲慢 歇斯底里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:10.00,0:28:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外地我还是能准确把握自己给人的印象的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:15.69,0:28:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳你不用去考虑怎么做才像祐巳该做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:18.36,0:28:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按自己想的去做就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:20.79,0:28:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样做的结果就是祐巳的风格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.49,0:28:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对祐巳来说 我觉得这样就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:28.14,0:28:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.50,0:28:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩只看到你的外在而喜欢上你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:33.22,0:28:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许外在可以成为联系人与人之间的细线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:36.97,0:28:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只有外在是脆弱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.05,0:28:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要称做羁绊还远远不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:42.28,0:28:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 我喜欢上姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:45.95,0:28:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初只是因为看到您用风琴弹奏万福玛莉亚的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:51.55,0:28:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.33,0:28:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但重要的东西却是深藏在内的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.16,0:28:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找到可不是件容易的事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:01.88,0:29:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳的脸颊 头发 声音 指尖 虽然这些我全部都喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:08.26,0:29:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不仅仅是因为喜欢外在而喜欢上你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:12.03,0:29:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更重要的是牵动着这些的 你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:16.84,0:29:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:18.68,0:29:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 眼睛看不到的部分哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:26.85,0:29:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 找到了看不到的部分?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:30.26,0:29:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:32.04,0:29:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 即使在寂静无声 漆黑一片的世界里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:36.60,0:29:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果祐巳在的话 一定马上就能知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:40.83,0:29:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 对了 假如祐巳卷入什么大事故里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:47.48,0:29:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被送进的医院里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.75,0:29:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算病床上躺着一千个埃及木乃伊似的全身绷带的伤患
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:59.28,0:30:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能够不出差错地一下子就找到祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:06.55,0:30:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 姐姐大人 这个比喻有点不吉利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.81,0:30:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但是 就是指到这种程度也不会把你认错的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:23.19,0:30:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:48.48,0:30:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.23,0:30:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.56,0:30:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者 还有泰山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:53.44,0:30:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:56.09,0:30:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么喧哗 真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.82,0:31:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是花寺学院吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:00.38,0:31:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去年来过 已经习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.69,0:31:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不对莉莉安的各位失礼 已经郑重宣布过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.65,0:31:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果出现什么问题 不仅是休学或退学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.61,0:31:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所属的社团也可能被撤销
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.79,0:31:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺学院的社团活动非常重视传统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.00,0:31:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果因为个人原因使得社团被撤销的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:21.18,0:31:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将是一生都不能再踏入花寺大门的耻辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:25.15,0:31:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很有精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:33.60,0:31:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是蔷薇大人们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.65,0:31:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.92,0:31:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.91,0:31:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只给我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.92,0:32:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是我们中只有祐巳最像小孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:05.51,0:32:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不好呢 祐巳喜欢甜食吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:09.01,0:32:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只熊猫一定也知道这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.76,0:32:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的话 给我怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:15.72,0:32:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这是人家给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.91,0:32:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别边走边吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.02,0:32:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.48,0:32:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推理小说同好会?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.22,0:32:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:30.48,0:32:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:33.74,0:32:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如上所说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:35.71,0:32:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位蔷薇大人为登上了望台的挑战者们审查问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.58,0:32:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在回答正确的同学的问题卡上贴上正确标记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:45.41,0:32:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间是两点到三点半之间的九十分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:49.35,0:32:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还有什么问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.87,0:32:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 一切就交给花寺的同学们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:55.75,0:32:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位花蕾就拜托协助蔷薇大人们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.89,0:33:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要换上花寺的校服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:02.36,0:33:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 怕站在了望台上穿着莉莉安的校服的花蕾们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.90,0:33:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被误认作蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:12.54,0:33:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们就在外面等候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:29.30,0:33:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袖子可以卷起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.46,0:33:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裤管果然太长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:39.08,0:33:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子 带了回形针吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:41.48,0:33:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的 不过不够三个人用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:44.39,0:33:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有鞋跟高点的鞋子就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:49.86,0:33:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就借这个一用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.35,0:33:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是木屐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:54.96,0:33:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 也行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.57,0:33:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发怎么办? 放下来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.00,0:33:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:02.48,0:34:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发翘起来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:04.61,0:34:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳带着毛巾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.34,0:34:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:11.93,0:34:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:13.04,0:34:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和木屐很配呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:14.86,0:34:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:16.13,0:34:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:19.11,0:34:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 祐巳和小麒一个样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:22.54,0:34:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要那样!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.86,0:34:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光相貌 说话也一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:28.61,0:34:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:33.03,0:34:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 是谁把这么大的箱子放在出口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:36.62,0:34:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什么时候有的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.41,0:34:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才还没有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:40.30,0:34:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是在送往别处的途中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:45.74,0:34:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「警告」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:47.00,0:34:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「三十分钟以内不来取走箱子的话 我们将自行处理」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:51.27,0:34:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「并且主人也要有受到相应处罚的觉悟」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:56.67,0:35:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「花寺学院高中学生会长 福泽祐麒」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:00.52,0:35:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:39.18,0:35:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道要用那个梯子爬上去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:43.19,0:35:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 梯子是我们用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.37,0:35:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也准备好了阶梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:50.56,0:35:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阶梯只有一个 请一个个来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.58,0:35:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我先来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:38.29,0:36:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.87,0:36:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 说了我可以的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:42.85,0:36:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也想上去试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:46.44,0:36:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了望台上面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:47.90,0:36:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我想到底在上面会是什么感觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.90,0:36:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 一起爬上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:55.98,0:36:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:03.82,0:37:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这就是姐姐大人的座位呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:11.16,0:37:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很牢固的 没问题的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.35,0:37:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 没问题呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:19.74,0:37:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 祐巳 要留在这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:22.27,0:37:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一会儿下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.26,0:37:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阶梯要拿走了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:26.01,0:37:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我用梯子下去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:28.07,0:37:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用梯子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:29.34,0:37:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没穿裙子 不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:33.58,0:37:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳看起来只是裙子的问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.37,0:37:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厉害呢 这么高 我用梯子是无论如何也下不去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:54.09,0:37:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学 马上就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:58.29,0:38:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 花寺合战第二关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:02.24,0:38:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉安阵 开战!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:17.12,0:38:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐…祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:19.75,0:38:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.65,0:38:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 第一个上来的 体操部的石黑同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.04,0:38:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到一百号的问题中 到底选哪个呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.36,0:38:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.60,0:38:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:34.90,0:38:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原子序数是七的元素是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.02,0:38:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:39.65,0:38:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:04.15,0:39:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 在找什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.13,0:39:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:07.73,0:39:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过算了 好像留在学生会室中的包里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:12.33,0:39:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:14.25,0:39:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦 我还有手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:16.39,0:39:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去去就来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.75,0:39:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古文课铃木老师的太太叫什么名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.82,0:39:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学 怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.96,0:39:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人忘了拿的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:43.48,0:39:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.86,0:39:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛那边怎么样了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.99,0:39:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常激烈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.09,0:39:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代我为祥子大人加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:53.72,0:39:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 爱丽丝留在这里看守也辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:02.15,0:40:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 福泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:09.89,0:40:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.65,0:40:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那里有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:33.52,0:40:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人可是你小心再小心 还是防不胜防的危险存在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:56.40,0:40:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳该回来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:00.45,0:41:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 还没到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:02.24,0:41:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:03.90,0:41:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:05.77,0:41:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷路了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:07.84,0:41:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很显眼 迷路应该不会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:12.07,0:41:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:15.38,0:41:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找找 祐麒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:17.44,0:41:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:19.85,0:41:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是她的弟弟吧 难道不担心祐巳吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:24.36,0:41:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学 您怎么这样说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:29.63,0:41:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:32.49,0:41:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了 快去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.92,0:41:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的话没听到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:44.75,0:41:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了? 小麒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:46.38,0:41:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活动还没结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:48.45,0:41:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学担心祐巳 无论如何也要我来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:53.01,0:41:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳来过了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:54.48,0:41:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不过是很久之前哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.36,0:42:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:01.38,0:42:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:02.81,0:42:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 祐巳同学离开房间后 走廊上突然很吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:08.00,0:42:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我开门看到来拿纸箱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:13.06,0:42:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁拿走的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:15.07,0:42:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 大概是四个人抬走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:18.69,0:42:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬空箱子要用四个人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.33,0:42:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:27.08,0:42:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定就是这个「难道」了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:35.51,0:42:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和祐麒搞混了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:37.23,0:42:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:42.44,0:42:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道该如何道歉才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:45.33,0:42:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为长得那么像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:47.33,0:42:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的弟弟也常常这样用头巾包着头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.33,0:42:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么推理小说同好会要绑架学生会长?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:56.96,0:42:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这原因倒是说来话短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:00.09,0:43:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说来话长吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.55,0:43:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推理小说同好会以前可是很体面的社团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:06.10,0:43:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在成员却少了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.08,0:43:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果在学园祭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:09.68,0:43:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能成功举办让学生会刮目相看的活动的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.92,0:43:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生会全体成员就按约定加入同好会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:18.38,0:43:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样成员人数增加了 同好会就能升格成社团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:22.51,0:43:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们发行的同人志上刊登着这样的小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:28.61,0:43:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏洛克与小五郎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:30.23,0:43:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是杂志名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:32.93,0:43:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的学生会长之谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.49,0:43:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果小说上写的犯罪能在现实中实现的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:38.44,0:43:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:39.62,0:43:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:41.17,0:43:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 这个小说就是犯罪预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:44.95,0:43:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后没有觉察到这点的学生会一定会对我们刮目相看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:49.13,0:43:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是把我和祐麒搞混后 这个计划已经失败了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.41,0:43:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:56.23,0:43:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快把我送到了望台那里去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:02.62,0:44:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:04.01,0:44:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:05.58,0:44:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们绑架了莉莉安学生会成员的事情一定会曝光的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.78,0:44:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在说不定已经乱成一团了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.88,0:44:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样社团会被撤销的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.45,0:44:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会对别人说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.83,0:44:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果你从这里出去时被人看到的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:22.32,0:44:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在终于有些明白绑匪杀掉人质的心情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.90,0:44:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 长相也被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:29.70,0:44:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你们都在想些什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:34.13,0:44:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有能不被人看见而让你离开的办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.27,0:44:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 小麒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:54.54,0:44:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏木学长 为什么会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:58.62,0:44:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:00.18,0:45:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳? 不在这里哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:03.87,0:45:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:07.45,0:45:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长 请让一让
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:16.05,0:45:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:17.76,0:45:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小麒 我知道推理小说同好会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:21.33,0:45:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出了怎么惩罚都不过分的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:24.90,0:45:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想包庇这样的学弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:27.74,0:45:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这次看在祐巳的份上原谅他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:31.96,0:45:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:32.81,0:45:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 她真是个好孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:36.26,0:45:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让这件事尽量不公开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.29,0:45:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够做到那种程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:41.49,0:45:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:44.35,0:45:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细经过待会儿再来问你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:47.12,0:45:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 祐巳现在在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:49.95,0:45:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在哪里错过了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:53.04,0:45:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳在你进来之前就自己走了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:57.98,0:45:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 难道是那只熊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:59.16,0:46:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 光发发糖果还是吸引不了客人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:23.27,0:46:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:54.73,0:46:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 祐巳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:03.99,0:47:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.37,0:47:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这副模样也能认出是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.86,0:47:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:15.78,0:47:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能在比赛结束前回来 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:19.24,0:47:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 虽然担心这副模样让姐姐大人知道了会有什么表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:25.72,0:47:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是又等不及去换 心里只想着快点见到姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:34.68,0:47:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人向我证明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:38.08,0:47:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「即使在寂静无声 漆黑一片的世界里」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:41.11,0:47:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「如果祐巳在的话一定马上就能知道的」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:45.81,0:47:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:50.12,0:47:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「还有 对了 假如祐巳卷入什么大事故里面」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:57.14,0:47:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「在被送进的医院里」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:59.41,0:48:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「就算病床上躺着一千个埃及木乃伊似的全身绷带的伤患」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:07.93,0:48:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我也能够不出差错地一下子就找到祐巳」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:13.57,0:48:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「就是指到这种程度也不会把你认错的意思」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:21.69,0:48:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「姐姐大人…」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:33.64,0:48:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「别担心 我会一直支持祐巳的」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:38.90,0:48:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:55.51,0:48:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「姐姐大人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:59.03,0:49:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪里也找不到比这更美好的幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:36.99,0:50:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺学院的学园祭虽然平安结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:40.50,0:50:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是我们莉莉安女学园的体育祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:44.13,0:50:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有件让我担心的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:47.01,0:50:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是可南子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:49.56,0:50:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了像吵架分开的样子 让人放心不下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:54.42,0:50:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可南子和我在体育祭那天打了一场赌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:59.92,0:51:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 就好好做个了断吧 祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:03.23,0:51:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.60,0:51:06.02,next,NTP,0,0,0,,LADY GO{\fad(800,0)}{\pos(766,420)}
